    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Alaska\nAirlines\nHas Some\nConvenient\nNew Space in\nSan Francisco\nAlaska\nAirlines\nAlaska Airlines\nasia\nAirlines",
      "We've moved Alaska Airlines\ngate location and ticket counter in the\nSan Francisco airport to make\ntraveling easier and faster\nfor our friends. Our new departure gate is 51,\nthe first gate off the concourse on Pier F. It's just a\nshort walk from our ticket counter.\nAlso enjoy fast baggage pick-up at TWA carousel 4\ndirectly below our ticket counter on the\nlower level. And now air cargo shipping is easier too,\nfrom the TWA air freight office.\nEasier to reach,\ncoming and going.\nLess congestion too.\nPIER\nIER\nPIER\nCENTRAL TERMINAL\nPIER\nNORTH\nTERMINAL\nAlaska Airlines\nPIER\nSOUTH\nTERMINAL\nGARAGE\nARRIVALS\nDEPARTURES\nPIER\nFF\nPIER\nROTUNDA\n2007.011.316"
    ],
